<figureCitation box="[159,227,1776,1801]" captionStart="FIGURE 6" captionStartId="7.[151,250,1388,1410]" captionTargetBox="[161,1433,629,1364]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[151,1436,628,1364]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURE 6. Colurella cf. psammophila. A, C. Left lateral view. B, E. Ventral view. D. Dorsal view. Scale bar: A–E: 50 µm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2647252/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="481">Fig. 6</figureCitation>
